	<h2>Bahamas</h2>
	<a href="http://www.cs.mun.ca/~g25gal/CS_Travel_1_C/WebContent/imgs/temp.JPG"><img alt="Bahamas" src="http://www.cs.mun.ca/~g25gal/CS_Travel_1_C/WebContent/imgs/temp_thumb.jpg"></a>
	<p>This seven-night package covers your airfare and hotel expenses at the stunning 
	Royal Bahamas Hotel, leaving you free to spend your time in the Bahamas 
	however you want. The Bahamas has much to offer in the way of tourist 
	activities, from active adventures like diving and playing sports to more 
	relaxing diversions such as being pampered at a spa or enjoying some of the 
	Bahamas' world-class beaches. For an idea of where to start, TripAdvisor.com 
	rates the Bahamas' top 5 tourist destinations as [ordered list: Castaway Cay, 
	Pink Sands Beach, Food Tours, The Tiki Bikini Hut, Gold Sands Beach] 
	Cost: $3500.</p>
